Ajaxfilemanager
Version: 0.2
Built with: Django 1.5 - Python 2.7.3

This ajaxfilemanager based on python-django!

Released with Django 1.5

Install
=======

It's easy:

 1. Copy the complete repo(latest release in master) into your project folder
 2. Add the App to the INSTALLED_APPS
 3. Copy the "templates" directory into your template-directory
 4. Add a URL-Rule to your urls.py in the django-site-root
    Example:
    url(r^'ajaxfilemanager/', include('ajaxfilemanager.urls')),
 5. Ensure that you activate 'staticfiles'
Finish!

Usage
=====
Serve to 'http://your.server.adress/ajaxfilemanager'. You will be redirect to 'http://your.server.adress/ajaxfilemanager/?path=/'.
The Path Syntax in the URL is simple. The '/' is the ajaxfm_media_root. The rest is the original path.    
